50|$|Certain ballparks {{have their}} outfield bullpens in unusual configurations. Petco Park {{features}} <b>the</b> home <b>bullpen</b> behind <b>the</b> outfield fence and <b>the</b> visitor's <b>bullpen</b> behind that and one level higher. <b>The</b> visitor's <b>bullpen</b> {{was moved to}} this location from foul territory after the 2012 season.|$|R
