5|$|In 2007, Greinke {{returned}} to the Royals rotation {{at the start of}} the season, but was assigned to <b>the</b> <b>bullpen</b> in early May. In 52 appearances (14 starts), Grienke finished 2007 with a 7-7 record and a 3.69 ERA.|$|E
5|$|With the Rockies, Affeldt {{was used}} {{exclusively}} out of <b>the</b> <b>bullpen.</b> He got his only save {{of the season}} on September 19 in a 124 win over the San Francisco Giants. Affeldt finished the 2006 season with a 6.20 ERA in fiftynine games.|$|E
